title: What Do You Believe?
itunes:title: What Do You Believe?
description:
Episode 517 - Your world is nothing more than a set a belief systems that you are holding on to. That being said, when was the last time you stepped outside of yourself and looked at your belief systems, your habits and your patterns and evaluated them? In this episode, I dive into the strategy of how to self evaluate your beliefs and how to change them if necessary!
